{"tid":633027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英直男服藥後戀上男人 「我對女人的性慾無咗」","createTime":"2018-04-18T02:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T04:37:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"745905d90ce2620e93cb59adf7fa0b69678f10a5","tid":633027,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"「我發現我對女人的性慾消失得無影無蹤，然後我很想得到男性的注意&hellip;&hellip;」英國23歲男子珀迪（Scott Purdy）娓娓道來他的性向改變經過，他歸咎止痛藥普瑞巴林（Pregabalin，別名Lyrica），冀公開自己經歷，讓其他病人明白風險。<br />\n<br />\n珀迪坦言，自己一直是「血氣方剛的異性戀者」，很享受跟女性約會，服藥前也有一個交往了半年的女朋友，但自從忍受不了另一種止痛藥可待因（Codeine）的副作用後，獲醫生處方普瑞巴林舒緩他斷腳的痛楚，自此性向有翻天覆地的變化。<br />\n<br />\n「我從來不會對男性感興趣，最多是小時候曾感到好奇，但我服此藥後數星期突然有大變化，跟她說我已不再覺得她性感得吸引我。」珀迪說，當時唯有跟當時女友分手，再與網上結織的男性拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n為何認定普瑞巴林改變其性向呢？他說：「我試過停藥數星期，那對男人的慾望又消失了。」不過他其後選擇繼續服藥，還樂於成為同性戀者，他說：「我現在很快樂，我希望繼續服藥，因為我很滿意這性向，這樣令我感覺很開放，很解放似的&hellip;&hellip;我沒有為此發怒，因為那只是讓我做回自己。」"},{"pid":"283a20dad13270ea80af5e147a56693e192a5ec5","tid":633027,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:45:38.000Z","msg":"不過，珀迪認為有必要公開經歷告誡他人，他警告：「若然未來有任何人獲處方這藥物，我覺得他們最好知道這藥物可能帶來的改變。」<br />\n<br />\n普瑞巴林由藥廠輝瑞（Pfizer）生產，可用作治療癲癇、與大腦相關的疼痛以及廣泛性焦慮症，已知的副作用包括性慾下降及情緒變得反覆。輝瑞發言人回應此個案時指出，目前全球有多達3400萬人服此藥，強調輝瑞永遠會以藥物安全為首要考慮，他說：「如果你服藥期間遇到任何非預期的副作用，我建議你即時向你的醫生或其他醫學專業人士，例如護士或護理員報告。」"},{"pid":"cff8c20013be825c80b9aa71642aa8e40f452945","tid":633027,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180417/large/1523946681_b5cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523946681_b5cf.jpg&h=cd270397&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"942766669d5f8f0c72341b7dc55ce725a226a692","tid":633027,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180418/58082584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58082584&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=24691800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F58082584&h=e26f7bd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180418/58082584</a>"},{"pid":"4634a64cb74a256c1108842a78e19b9acabfe999","tid":633027,"uid":13160,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"Gay既食左會唔會變番直？"},{"pid":"beb2785b440a17917280d2a7f2b1d1ba75dac2ca","tid":633027,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"新藥面世"},{"pid":"396f99317111787eb89f5aed14f9bc0e4d3eb075","tid":633027,"uid":52459,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"他的人生可以complete了"},{"pid":"583d77747336d74ac6b0dbef020f8da98e43eb32","tid":633027,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb055a944b1d5be117c1fd0f3fe759ecc1c171d","tid":633027,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eae71d32574ea72ad3729ed5e551140c356e9f","tid":633027,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"396f99317111787eb89f5aed14f9bc0e4d3eb075","tid":633027,"uid":52459,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"他的人生可以complete了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"被問到是0定1 他回答 當然是1啦 哈哈"},{"pid":"a00cd3f7bdaee00852e9616ae01a717462b9ea13","tid":633027,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dis